data.description: If a beautiful home with an in-ground pool, outdoor kitchen, detached garage in a quiet subdivision is what you are looking for, THIS IS IT!  This beautiful 2,800 s.f. home offers (4) bedrooms, (2.5) bathrooms, large bonus, formal dining room and is perfectly situated on a .75 acre lot with mature trees.  Entry, family room and formal dining all have gorgeous wood floors and high ceilings.  Formal dining room has tray ceiling, wainscoting and crown molding.  The family room is large with fireplace, and windows overlooking the pool.  This kitchen would make any culinary enthusiast happy with its tile flooring, breakfast room, breakfast bar, SS appliances, tons of cabinets and lots of countertop space! The primary bedroom features hardwood floors, a tray ceiling crown molding and small study office.  The master salon bath has a walk-in shower and jacuzzi tub.   The laundry room is super-sized, with a storage closet and enough room for another refrigerator or a freezer.  This home has stairway with lovely wrought iron railing and stately arches throughout.  Upstairs, you have three additional bedrooms plus a bonus and full bathroom.  Outside, is the real oasis with the in-ground saltwater pool, mature trees and outdoor kitchen with small bathroom.  The detached garage is 24x30. The only thing missing from this home is you!  Schedule your tour today!
